description: Andada is a text font with an organic-slab serif, hybrid style, a solid design of medium stroke contrast. This font has received an award at the Ibero-America Design Biennial. The Biennial has been shown in Spain, Argentina, Chile, El Salvador, Uruguay, Bolivia, Colombia and Venezuela. Designed by Carolina Giovagnoli for Huerta Tipográfica.
